Package: gmeowgts
Type: Package
Title: R Wrapper for the GTS C ABI
Version: 0.9.4
Depends: R (>= 4.3)
Authors@R: c(
    person("Blackcat Informatics", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "paudley@blackcatinformatics.ca")
    )
Author: Blackcat Informatics
Maintainer: Blackcat Informatics <paudley@blackcatinformatics.ca>
Description: Provides R bindings to the GTS C ABI backed by the Rust
    implementation in gmeow-gts. The package exposes archive metadata,
    validation, RDF/N-Quads conversion, and files-profile helpers while
    requiring an externally installed libgts shared library at build and
    runtime.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: libgts shared library from the gmeow-gts C ABI; set
    GTS_LIB_DIR to the directory containing libgts when it is not installed in
    a standard system library path.
URL: https://blackcatinformatics.ca/projects/gts,
    https://github.com/Blackcat-Informatics/gmeow-gts
BugReports: https://github.com/Blackcat-Informatics/gmeow-gts/issues
